Company Overview of First Long Island Investors, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
First Long Island Investors, LLC, a wealth management company, provides investment advisory and financial services for high-net-worth individuals, families, and institutions. It offers strategic asset allocation-individualized solutions; security-cash, fixed income, and absolute return strategies; capital growth-hedged equity, core equity, and diversified equity services; opportunity investments-private equity, real estate, and real assets services; and wealth administration services. The company was founded in 1983 and is based in Jericho, New York.


