First Long Island Investors, LLC Key Developments

First of Long Island Corp. Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend, Payable on January 13, 2017
Dec 21 16
First of Long Island Corp. announced that it will distribute a quarterly cash dividend of $0.14 per share, down from a prior quarterly distribution of $0.21 per share. The dividend is payable on Jan. 13, 2017 to holders of record on Jan. 3, 2017.


First Long Island Investors Names Lawrence Waldman as Managing Director
Apr 6 16
Lawrence Waldman was appointed as managing director of First Long Island Investors. Waldman, who currently serves as an advisor to EisnerAmper and as a board member and audit committee chairman for several companies, is a former managing partner of KPMG’s Long Island office.


