About
First Long Island Investors, Llc is located at the address 58 Knollwood Dr in Carle Place, New York 11514.  First Long Island Investors, Llc has an annual sales volume of 1M – 1,999,999.  .For more information contact Laura  Brazicki,   or  go to www.fliinvestors.comFirst Long Island Investors, Llc provides Corporate Services, Disability Income, Institutional Services to it's customers.  For maps and directions to First Long Island Investors, Llc view the map to the right.  For reviews of First Long Island Investors, Llc see below.









